dc_title_s: Commercial Biodiesel Production Plants: United States, Fall 2014
dc_description_s: This point dataset represents the locations of commercial biodiesel production plants in the United States. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Fall Quarter update (Update 1017). This shapefie can be used for locating and analysing existing commercial biodiesel production plants in the United States. Hart Energy Publishing (2015). Commercial Biodiesel Production Plants: United States, Fall 2014. Hart Energy Publishing. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/zm624wt5578. This release is intended to replace all previous datasets This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
